    {
      "id": 139057,
      "postNumber": 1,
      "createdAt": "2023-08-14T23:25:39.702Z",
      "author": "Ross.ballard (Ross)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>When I make a Sub Item I can Make a status based on sub items status but if i collapse the group the status of all the sub-statuses aren’t collated like they are with the sub status.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/c/4c0f0ff33c18809edf04fc06de67145cf22ac4b4.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2023-08-09 at 09.45.29\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/c/4c0f0ff33c18809edf04fc06de67145cf22ac4b4_2_690x102.jpeg\" alt=\"WhatsApp Image 2023-08-09 at 09.45.29\" width=\"690\" height=\"102\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">WhatsApp Image 2023-08-09 at 09.45.29</span><span class=\"informations\">720×107 5.16 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/f/9febd1bf317939101cb2d28ac8c5a8c26f708d90.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2023-08-09 at 09.45.10\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/f/9febd1bf317939101cb2d28ac8c5a8c26f708d90.jpeg\" alt=\"WhatsApp Image 2023-08-09 at 09.45.10\" width=\"690\" height=\"449\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">WhatsApp Image 2023-08-09 at 09.45.10</span><span class=\"informations\">693×451 31.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 139205,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2023-08-15T09:52:22.560Z",
      "author": "divory (Dan Ivory)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/ross.ballard\">@Ross.ballard</a></p>\n<p>If you click on the 3 dot menu at the top of the status column and then go to “Settings”, then “Show column summary” this should show you a rolled up view of the item statuses. Note it is showing at the item level, not the subitem level.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/2/9268dfd009877f2f0d908a9f67c5df030c2b36d8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/9/2/9268dfd009877f2f0d908a9f67c5df030c2b36d8_2_690x88.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"88\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">776×100 5.63 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>See below for the settings option you need to use.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/d/6d480e8d4e14e3d84c41992b444b5475a495d61a.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"580\" height=\"379\" /></p>\n<p>Hope that helps!<br />\nDan</p>"
    }
  ]
